name: canstack
body:
The Canadian OpenStack Users Group, or CanStack, is passionate about working together across Canada to help make the [OpenStack](http://openstack.org) project a success.

Supported in part by [Cybera](https://cybera.ca) and the OpenStack Foundation, we help members by organizing meetups and providing remote video and audio conferencing capabilities.

Here are a few ways to contact members:

* [Blog](http://blog.canstack.ca)
* [Twitter](http://twitter.com/canstack)
* [Meetup Group](http://www.meetup.com/Canadian-OpenStack-Users-Group/)
* [IRC](irc://irc.freenode.com/canstack) - Freenode #canstack
* [Github](http://github.com/canstack)
